original_title: bounded in a nutshell, counting himself king of infinite space
overview: Dreamy, chopped up, and made up primarily of skies, water, pixels, walls, animals, and a robot who is very good at free throws, "Bounded in a Nutshell, Counting Himself King of Infinite Space" is a video diary composed of fragments shot throughout late July and August 2020.  Music by symphonic synergy All footage captured on an iPhone and edited by me
